   no sound spec can raise the kill score here.  The in-loop __CPROVER_assert
   index-bound invariants are written as the iteration-local images of each loop
   bound (they would kill the extra-iteration mutants at an adequate unwind); the
   value delivered under the bounded harness is that the function VERIFIES. */
